  m_Name: Frank too Frank Frank
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  characterSystem:
    characterName: Frank "too Frank" Frank
    hejFras: 'Get a load of this guy! '
    hejFrasEvent:
      Guid:
        Data1: -1179198396
        Data2: 1075289099
        Data3: -1747352392
        Data4: 1507341150
      Path: event:/Frank/Frank Hej
    firstQuestion:
      question: 'You seem like someone who you don''t want to cross! '
      answer: "That would be a fair assumption hi I\u2019m Frank but you can call
        me Frankie how\u2019s it goin?  "
    q1FollowUpQuestion1:
      question: 'How did a guy like you get in here? '
      answer: "Weeell you could say I got a \u201Cspecial\u201D invitation. And by
        special I mean I didn\u2019t get one. And by didn\u2019t get one I mean I
        broke in. And by broke in I mean\u2026 Well yeah that\u2019s exactly what
        I mean. "
    q1FollowUpQuestion2:
      question: "You\u2019re pretty Frank about your criminal activity. "
      answer: "Well they don\u2019t call me \u201Ctoo Frank\u201D Frank for nothin\u2019.
        Don\u2019t go telling now, that fat head constable over there has been giving
        me the side eye the whole evenin\u2019\u2026 "
    secondQuestion:
      question: ' Is that a paw print on your pants? '
      answer: "Oh, hehe yeah. My little pup can be quite a mess! I love him thou,
        I always take him on walks first thing in the mornin\u2019! "
    q2FollowUpQuestion1:
      question: 'You''re quite the softy! '
      answer: "Only with mah family and the broads! But when I\u2019m workin\u2019,
        I\u2019m the toughest guy in town! Speaking of which, you wouldn't know anything
        about a\u2026 \u201Cmissing\u201D person? Someone under our protection hasn\u2019t
        been seen in a while and I have a\u2026 suspicion\u2026 "
    q2FollowUpQuestion2:
      question: 'Missing person? Sounds like something for the police. '
      answer: "Now don\u2019t be hasty! Something has to be done\u2026 outside the
        law.. you get me? "
    thirdQuestion:
      question: 'What did you think of the hors d''oeuvres? '
      answer: "Oar deers the what now? I ain\u2019t no frog, I\u2019m a full blooded
        italian\u2019! Land of pasta, classical music and the trains are always on
        time! "
    q3FollowUpQuestion1:
      question: "I didn\u2019t pin you as a \u201Cclassical\u201D kinda guy. "
      answer: "Of course! I love that Vivaldi guy! Though I love a good swing a wig!
        I\u2019m quite the ducky shincracker on the dancefloor! "
    q3FollowUpQuestion2:
      question: 'Someone here you would fancy a dance with? '
      answer: "You flirtin\u2019 with me? Hehe, nah I\u2019m just pulling your leg,
        but I could go for a dance! "
    "hejD\xE5Fras": "Don\u2019t go telling nothin\u2019 now! "
